  <p>This service creates and approves Home Detention Curfews and licences for prisoners.</p>

  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How can I change what I can see and do in this service?</h2>

  <p>If you need to make a change to your own role, or that of someone else, to access different parts of this service, you should contact <a href="mailto:hdcdigitalservice@digital.justice.gov.uk">hdcdigitalservice@digital.justice.gov.uk.</p>

  <p>For all other problems, you should contact the helpdesk by calling 020 3788 4636, or #6598 from inside a prison.</p>
